result.execSummary:
The defendant Justin Marshall Holt was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Justin Marshall Holt is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Justin Marshall Holt was found guilty of Incest with Child by Stepparent, a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.06(1m).
  • Justin Marshall Holt was found guilty of Repeated Sexual Assault of Same Child (At Least 3 Violations of 1st or 2nd Degree Sexual Assault), a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.025(1)(e).
